      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver with character? This well-loved vehicle is ready for its next chapter! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years on the road, it still runs strong and offers a comfortable ride. It's a fantastic, budget-friendly option for anyone needing dependable transportation without the new-car price tag. Come see why this sturdy car still has plenty of miles left to give!",
