    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this superlative motorcar, preserved in a state that can only be described as showroom-quality. This vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer to acquire a specimen maintained to an uncompromising standard. Every aspect, from the flawless exterior finish to the immaculate interior appointments, reflects meticulous stewardship and a commitment to excellence. This is an investment-grade acquisition for those who demand nothing less than perfection in their automotive pursuits.",
      "price": 47900.0,
