    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-grade 2017 Porsche 718 Cayman S, finished in timeless Carrara White Metallic. This vehicle has been fastidiously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and has never encountered inclement weather. The exterior is indistinguishable from new, featuring a professional-grade ceramic coating that provides a deep, mirror-like luster and total paint protection. Inside, the Agate Grey leather interior is flawless; the bolsters show zero signs of entry wear, and the cabin retains its original factory aroma. Every surface, from the Alcantara headliner to the precision-stitched dashboard, is in showroom condition. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive Porsche dealership service history and recent multi-point inspections. It comes highly optioned with the Sport Chrono Package, PASM Sport Suspension, and 20-inch Carrera S wheels shod in brand-new Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-quality example that satisfies the most meticulous standards.",
